@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = ((v1 / wp.sin(v0 + 0.65)) - wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.28)))
    tmp = tmp
    v0 = (wp.sin((tmp + 0.88 / tmp + 0.96)) + 0.80)
    data[tid] = v0
